4553759d0c0738af5fa460adaaa012","tid":464793,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"我都成日有鼻敏感<br />\n好嚴重個隻<br />\n你有冇噴得多類固醇既副作用?"},{"pid":"c098c09b86c6ed2a247efb8888f4ba7db029f6a8","tid":464793,"uid":33623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地有冇試過 <br />\n打側向左邊訓, 左邊鼻塞,  打側向右邊訓, 右邊鼻塞,  打平訓, 兩邊都塞</blockquote><br />\n不嬲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf347c6bccfaae43984d722518a7ac38ba9034b","tid":464793,"uid":75466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點都要噴，唔噴就流鼻水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又冇流鼻水 同埋唔噴 一起身會狂打黑痴 超敏感</blockquote><br />\n唔噴會鼻塞 周身唔聚財<br />\n成日想捽個鼻"},{"pid":"6df811925b94cca34d1e8ec9e376d0073f93d5d4","tid":464793,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小心唔用會有反彈</blockquote><br />\n血管收縮劑至會<br />\n類固醇一黎唔會太大副作用 因為身體吸收唔多<br />\n上左癮就另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n類固醇唔會太大副作用 ?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ae2d2bf92bcb07b48587766f8ef1d674eeaf3c","tid":464793,"uid":75466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都成日有鼻敏感<br />\n好嚴重個隻<br />\n你有冇噴得多類固醇既副作用?</blockquote><br />\n基本上無 有部分人噴得多會流鼻血<br />\n因為噴得多會整薄左鼻黏膜（鼻黏膜薄左 鼻塞都減退）"},{"pid":"c3922b50e0d97b333995311930b6395f2c8ff5e0","tid":464793,"uid":75466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小心唔用會有反彈</blockquote><br />\n血管收縮劑至會<br />\n類固醇一黎唔會太大副作用 因為身體吸收唔多<br />\n上左癮就另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n類固醇唔會太大副作用 ?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n噴鼻唔會太大副作用 因為藥物只係停留係鼻腔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小朋友要注意 可能影響身高 （如果噴太多太密）"},{"pid":"a01e4ec0bfae98c0b5e9fc053d4796de85e9afb5","tid":464793,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:48:19.000Z","msg":"換多啲床單 枕頭套 清潔 入屋除鞋 唔好引到小強<br />\n<br />\n瞓要搵野撤住個頭<br />\n<br />\n嚴重鼻敏感要斷尾 唔係嘅話婚姻生活多樣野煩"},{"pid":"2309f03a6d5cf540cfa74a1cb325333dc99369bf","tid":464793,"uid":33612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:50:32.000Z","msg":"小學到而家用咗十三年<br />\n而家嘗試少用<br />\n塞到瞓唔到先每邊一下"},{"pid":"1a171fc1cdd5365fa377fdad1629423ba34da128","tid":464793,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:50:51.000Z","msg":"巴打是咪鼻敏感?<br />\n利申  以前個醫生叫我噴咗一陣驚依賴就冇噴"},{"pid":"3fa29bbcc36fd9cdd997cac4bba89dac0d27f185","tid":464793,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打是咪鼻敏感?<br />\n利申  以前個醫生叫我噴咗一陣驚依賴就冇噴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是 超強的鼻敏感 <br />\n<br />\n照過鼻鏡 醫生都嚇左一跳, 建議我做個手術切薄鼻甲內既鼻膜"},{"pid":"a7abcb7d6b148fe383ea4f46afb8846e990c525c","tid":464793,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學到而家用咗十三年<br />\n而家嘗試少用<br />\n塞到瞓唔到先每邊一下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係一噴就即通 <br />\n類固純O個D 要長期少少的"},{"pid":"726a48dac70ab9847000e7c9f3353e9e19edd073","tid":464793,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地有冇試過 <br />\n打側向左邊訓, 左邊鼻塞,  打側向右邊訓, 右邊鼻塞,  打平訓, 兩邊都塞</blockquote><br />\n不嬲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都是?! 巴打"},{"pid":"ffb7f95c81d1170b92acfcdf1e422612bf235e01","tid":464793,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小心唔用會有反彈</blockquote><br />\n血管收縮劑至會<br />\n類固醇一黎唔會太大副作用 因為身體吸收唔多<br /