/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你切左鼻膜咁有冇再腫 ?  你是鼻塞定鼻水?"},{"pid":"c2681dfab18ec0a1195920655910e0809e93a61c","tid":464793,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小心唔用會有反彈</blockquote><br />\n血管收縮劑至會<br />\n類固醇一黎唔會太大副作用 因為身體吸收唔多<br />\n上左癮就另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會太大副作用？<br />\n<br />\n你試下唔用一星期</blockquote><br />\n會有咩副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWithdrawal symptoms <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係咩?!"},{"pid":"aa220b1c103642f01db9d93a2140c245838d8dfc","tid":464793,"uid":33612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小學到而家用咗十三年<br />\n而家嘗試少用<br />\n塞到瞓唔到先每邊一下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係一噴就即通 <br />\n類固純O個D 要長期少少的</blockquote><br />\n噴咗感覺良好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經轉咗三隻藥<br />\n得一隻手術前用嘅係強效嘢"},{"pid":"5e0586854e986b25516917f2fe846c47aae35af7","tid":464793,"uid":24111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"小學開始塞 剩係噴類固醇 <br />\n又係唔噴就一啲都抖唔到氣 噴到廿幾歲<br />\n到上年終於正視個問題 睇耳鼻喉科 <br />\n醫生話我鼻骨s型 兩邊鼻甲增生肥大 話做手術就搞得掂<br />\n做完兩個禮拜 傷口都埋左口 但都只係通得5成<br />\n再過多一兩個月 又完全塞番晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似冇做過咁<br />\n問番醫生佢都好似冇撚晒辦法咁<br />\n依家變番繼續噴 幾個鐘噴一次 <br />\n得戈廿幾歲 都唔知點撚樣算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1e680a4a842d5f3c0822eec528662784dcda00","tid":464793,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:57:47.000Z","msg":"用鹽水洗鼻好D, 開頭一個星期唔會太大效果, 之後清左鼻腔D菌就會開始通, 再加適當運動就會好好多, 我就每個星期都會去游水, 而家訓覺唔會塞 ( 利伸:讀書時嚴重鼻敏感, 以為自己成日感冒 )"},{"pid":"40f6efd5fb8e213cc9dee10f5734115003fe9e91","tid":464793,"uid":75466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小心唔用會有反彈</blockquote><br />\n血管收縮劑至會<br />\n類固醇一黎唔會太大副作用 因為身體吸收唔多<br />\n上左癮就另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會太大副作用？<br />\n<br />\n你試下唔用一星期</blockquote><br />\n會有咩副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWithdrawal symptoms <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n噴左6、7年 有時無噴2星期都無出現藥物戒斷<br />\n好多時噴返都係心癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daeae42527f30cfff3f6f47f3d75bdaea1994c13","tid":464793,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:37:33.000Z","msg":"果陣好鍾意噴，噴到流晒鼻血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764629cdfaf115ecd699c661f2a94bef03f8adb8","tid":464793,"uid":75466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:52:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人噴budesonide"},{"pid":"1bbf8287a91a4f2f25a35ea9a4fc9de57814827d","tid":464793,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"以前成日鼻塞，keep 住噴nezel ，開頭好有效，之後越來越密,效用時間越來越短.知道奶野就停左轉睇中醫，停左半年加中葯調理慢慢好番，我果種係血氣唔通所以塞,之後做多左運動真係改善左好多"},{"pid":"9b8f660875741b5975f42fe34da9a23fad8f9437","tid":464793,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學開始塞 剩係噴類固醇 <br />\n又係唔噴就一啲都抖唔到氣 噴到廿幾歲<br />\n到上年終於正視個問題 睇耳鼻喉科 <br />\n醫生話我鼻骨s型 兩邊鼻甲增生肥大 話做手術就搞得掂<br />\n做完兩個禮拜 傷口都埋左口 但都只係通得5成<br />\n再過多一兩個月 又完全塞番晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似冇做過咁<br />\n問番醫生佢都好似冇撚晒辦法咁<br />\n依家變番繼續噴 幾個鐘噴一次 <b